## Configuration Checklist
- [ ] Select correct model tier: Large for complex tasks, 7B for edge/lightweight
- [ ] For EU data residency: confirm deployment is on EU infrastructure
- [ ] For self-hosted: confirm model weights are loaded and endpoint is running
- [ ] For multilingual tasks: specify target language in the prompt
- [ ] For fine-tuned models: confirm the correct fine-tuned checkpoint is loaded
- [ ] For code tasks: use Codestral via API rather than general Mistral models
